<BLOCK1><TI TOCID="II">ORDER</TI>
<P><BOLD>THIS MOTION</BOLD> made by the Attorney General of Ontario, the defendant, to strike the Statement of Claim and dismiss this action pursuant to Rule 21 for failing to disclose a reasonable cause of action was heard this day at 393 University Avenue, Toronto, Ontario.</P>
<P><BOLD>ON READING</BOLD> the motion record, supplementary motion record, factum, and books of authorities of the defendant, and the responding factum and books of authorities of the plaintiffs, and on hearing the submissions of counsel for the plaintiffs and the defendant,</P>
<P><BOLD>1. THIS COURT ORDERS</BOLD> that the plaintiffs' claim in negligence is struck.</P>
<P><BOLD>2. THIS COURT FURTHER ORDERS</BOLD> that the remainder of the defendant's motion to strike is dismissed.</P>
<P><BOLD>3. THIS COURT FURTHER ORDERS</BOLD> that there be no Order as to costs.</P>
<P>&ellip35; Chris Di Gregorio</P>
<P>Registrar</P></BLOCK1>
